{"tid":1774143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港反送中掀浪潮 你應該關心的2019五大人權事件","createTime":"2019-12-08T05:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T05:14:14.000Z","uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4398772a1ed256ac20eb3b7d19a02fbde5ef36","tid":1774143,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T05:04:06.000Z","msg":"香港反送中掀浪潮 你應該關心的2019五大人權事件<br />\n   <br />\n2019-12-08 12:00:00<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPjUIsKjzs0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPjUIsKjzs0&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7Ekc2t2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=3f688696\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPjUIsKjzs0</a><br />\n〔記者陳韋宗／綜合報導〕香港「反送中」事件促使全球關注香港人權及民主發展，民間人權陣線也選在12月8日呼應國際人權日，發起大遊行，呼籲香港政府履行國際人權責任。<br />\n<br />\n回顧2019年，「人權」已成網路搜尋熱門關鍵字之一；除了香港，包括智利、新疆等地的人權議題，也都讓國際更加關注執政當局對人權的迫害。<br />\n<br />\n此外，聯合國今年呼籲各國重視空氣污染對人造成的危害，應將空氣污染視為一種「人權威脅」；台灣也在今年完成一項重要的維護人權工作，贏得國際的肯定。<br />\n<br />\n這則新聞影片將帶讀者快速回顧，2019年五件重大的國際人權事件，到底發生了些什麼？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zy7cUaL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzy7cUaL.jpg&h=93178b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港反送中、智利血腥鎮壓等事件，掀起全球對人權的關注。（路透）"},{"pid":"9744c7aa5f5e25c66c8bd3dcd3349adc907c5e53","tid":1774143,"uid":175590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">3點鐘 維園見 早D出門口呀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f83da84de2bf97c85a9a715ec1a7549964349e3","tid":1774143,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9744c7aa5f5e25c66c8bd3dcd3349adc907c5e53","tid":1